  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients who are new to a discussion about the common methods of managing
             musculoskeletal pain, over the age of 18, native English speakers

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Patient with a previous orthopaedic surgery or musculoskeletal pain consultation,
             patients without the capacity to give consent, chronic narcotic users. Patients with
             a severe mental, visual, auditory or tactile impairment.
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
